trans-unit.source: The ActiveDirectoryObjectExistsException class exception is thrown when an Active Directory Domain Services object is created and that object already exists in the underlying directory store.
trans-unit.target: 建立 Active Directory 網域服務物件，該物件已經存在於基礎目錄存放區時，會擲回 ActiveDirectoryObjectExistsException 類別例外狀況。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryObjectExistsException"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryObjectExistsException"></xref>類別。
